From 2b57431007e91034c2976a3a6fe76ddf40a1c8a7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: VTK Compatibility <vtk@vtk.org>
Date: Thu, 30 Apr 2026 22:22:11 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] macOS: Add gcc-14 and 10.5/10.6 SDK compatibility

Add compatibility for building VTK's Cocoa backend with gcc (non-clang)
compilers and older macOS SDKs (10.5/10.6).

Key changes:
- Add __has_feature fallback for gcc compatibility
- Add portable VTK_DIAG_OFF/VTK_DIAG_ON macros for diagnostic pragmas
- Lower minimum SDK requirement from 10.7 to 10.5
- Add helper functions for 10.7+ backing scale factor APIs:
  * vtkCocoaConvertPointToBacking/FromBacking
  * vtkCocoaConvertRectToBacking/FromBacking
  * vtkCocoaBackingScaleFactor
  * vtkCocoaWindowConvertRectToBacking/FromBacking
  * vtkCocoaScreenConvertRectToBacking/FromBacking
- Replace @[] array literal with [NSArray arrayWithObject:] for gcc
- Replace #pragma clang diagnostic with portable VTK_DIAG macros
- Replace fast enumeration (for-in) with NSEnumerator for gcc

Files modified:
- Rendering/UI/vtkCocoaMacOSXSDKCompatibility.h
- Rendering/UI/vtkCocoaRenderWindowInteractor.mm
- Rendering/OpenGL2/vtkCocoaGLView.mm
- Rendering/OpenGL2/vtkCocoaRenderWindow.mm
